---
title: Buttermilk Biscuits & Pork Sausage Gravy with Fried Eggs & Sweet Potato Hash
description: For a hearty, comforting meal, look no further than our easy homemade pork sausage gravy spooned over flaky, freshly baked biscuits. Top this enticing Southern-style classic with eggs fried just the way you like them, then serve alongside roasted sweet potato hash with onion and green pepper (plus a splash of your favorite hot sauce, if you like!).
